The PCRE library is a set of functions that implement regular expression pattern matching using the same syntax and semantics as Perl 5.

* Site: http://www.pcre.org/
* License: BSD

Release Notes:

* Upgraded to version 8.32

Install with Rudix command line:

	sudo rudix install pcre

Basic usage and help:

	pcregrep foo *.c
	pcre-config --cflags --libs
